# Contributing

Welcome! This initiative aims to create a curated list of companies that are open to hiring talent from Costa Rica :costa_rica:. By contributing to this project, you can help build a valuable resource for job seekers in Costa Rica and promote job opportunities within the country.

Contributing to this project is easy! Follow these simple steps:

## 1. Fork the Repository

Fork the repository by clicking the "Fork" button at the top right of this page. This will create a copy of the project in your GitHub account.

## 2. Edit the Markdown File

Go to the "README.md" file in your forked repository. This is where the list of companies is maintained. You can add as many companies as you like in alphabetical order. Please, follow the existing format.

## 3. Commit Changes

Create a new branch for this commit. Provide a brief description of the changes you made and commit.

## 4. Create a Pull Request

## 5. Wait for Review

Your pull request will be reviewed by project maintainers. If everything looks good, it will be merged into the main project.

Thank you for contributing to the project and helping job seekers find opportunities in Costa Rica! Your contributions are greatly appreciated.

If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out in the ["Issues"](https://github.com/dfernandeza/hiring-in-cr/issues) section of the repository.

Happy contributing! ðŸŒŸ